text: Five little fishies in the deep blue sea
Mommy says “Children, please listen to me!”
A big hungry shark is swimming about
And there’ll only be four fishies if you don’t watch out!
Four little fishies in the deep blue sea
Mommy says “Children, please listen to me!”
A big hungry shark is swimming about
And there’ll only be three fishies if you don’t watch out!
Three little fishies in the deep blue sea
Mommy says “Children, please listen to me!”
A big hungry shark is swimming about
And there’ll only be two fishies if you don’t watch out!
Two little fishies in the deep blue sea
Mommy says “Children, please listen to me!”
A big hungry shark is swimming about
And there’ll only be one fishy if you don’t watch out!
One little fishy in the deep blue sea
Mommy says “Fishy, please listen to me!”
A big hungry shark is swimming about
And there won’t be any fishies if you don’t watch out!
Five little fishies in the deep blue sea
Mommy says “I’m so glad you listened to me!”
A big hungry shark is swimming about
But we are all still together cause you all watched out!
